This is a reddit bot that will scan through newly posted comments in posts in /r/all and compare each word of the post
to a dictionary of commonly misspelled words. If any of the words match it will reply to the comment with the following
usage: 

  - Multiple words
    EDIT: words.. +word+*, +word+*
  - One word
    EDIT: word.. +word+*

1. bundle install in app dir
2. ruby grammarnazi.rb
3. enter creds for account to use
